{"id":"from-one-to-more","title":"From One to More: Contextual Part Latents for 3D Generation","venue":"ICCV 2025","task":"part-aware-generation","summary":"Decomposes objects into contextual part latents for coherent part-aware generation and editing.","paper":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.08772"}
